[
  {
    "content": "Thank you so much, Chris.",
    "duration": 1191,
    "startTime": 3337,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "And it's truly a great honor\nto have the opportunity",
    "duration": 3950,
    "startTime": 4552,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to come to this stage twice;\nI'm extremely grateful.",
    "duration": 3004,
    "startTime": 8526,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I have been blown away by this conference,",
    "duration": 3534,
    "startTime": 11554,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and I want to thank all of you\nfor the many nice comments",
    "duration": 5668,
    "startTime": 15112,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "about what I had to say the other night.",
    "duration": 2172,
    "startTime": 20804,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And I say that sincerely,",
    "duration": 2875,
    "startTime": 23000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "partly because (Mock sob)",
    "duration": 1964,
    "startTime": 25899,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I need that.",
    "duration": 1151,
    "startTime": 27887,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 5857,
    "startTime": 29062,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Put yourselves in my position.",
    "duration": 1921,
    "startTime": 34943,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 6528,
    "startTime": 36888,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I flew on Air Force Two for eight years.",
    "duration": 2557,
    "startTime": 43440,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1955,
    "startTime": 46021,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Now I have to take off my shoes\nor boots to get on an airplane!",
    "duration": 3364,
    "startTime": 48000,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2705,
    "startTime": 51388,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Applause)",
    "duration": 6448,
    "startTime": 54117,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I'll tell you one quick story",
    "duration": 1723,
    "startTime": 60589,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "to illustrate what\nthat's been like for me.",
    "duration": 3119,
    "startTime": 62336,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1521,
    "startTime": 65479,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "It's a true story --\nevery bit of this is true.",
    "duration": 2420,
    "startTime": 67024,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Soon after Tipper and I left the --\n(Mock sob) White House --",
    "duration": 3585,
    "startTime": 70158,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2018,
    "startTime": 73767,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "we were driving from our home\nin Nashville to a little farm we have",
    "duration": 4915,
    "startTime": 75809,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "50 miles east of Nashville.",
    "duration": 1991,
    "startTime": 80748,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Driving ourselves.",
    "duration": 1490,
    "startTime": 84000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2462,
    "startTime": 85514,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I know it sounds like\na little thing to you, but --",
    "duration": 2717,
    "startTime": 88000,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 5469,
    "startTime": 90741,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I looked in the rear-view mirror",
    "duration": 5707,
    "startTime": 96234,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "and all of a sudden it just hit me.",
    "duration": 3206,
    "startTime": 101965,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "There was no motorcade back there.",
    "duration": 1636,
    "startTime": 105195,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2654,
    "startTime": 106855,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "You've heard of phantom limb pain?",
    "duration": 1993,
    "startTime": 109533,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 4812,
    "startTime": 111550,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "This was a rented Ford Taurus.",
    "duration": 4216,
    "startTime": 116386,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2504,
    "startTime": 120626,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "It was dinnertime,",
    "duration": 2006,
    "startTime": 123154,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "and we started looking for a place to eat.",
    "duration": 2920,
    "startTime": 125184,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We were on I-40.",
    "duration": 1405,
    "startTime": 128588,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We got to Exit 238, Lebanon, Tennessee.",
    "duration": 3197,
    "startTime": 130017,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We got off the exit,\nwe found a Shoney's restaurant.",
    "duration": 3688,
    "startTime": 133238,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Low-cost family restaurant chain,\nfor those of you who don't know it.",
    "duration": 4039,
    "startTime": 136950,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We went in and sat down at the booth,\nand the waitress came over,",
    "duration": 4435,
    "startTime": 141877,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "made a big commotion over Tipper.",
    "duration": 1986,
    "startTime": 146336,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 2463,
    "startTime": 148346,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "She took our order, and then went\nto the couple in the booth next to us,",
    "duration": 3420,
    "startTime": 150833,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "and she lowered her voice so much,",
    "duration": 2104,
    "startTime": 154277,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I had to really strain to hear\nwhat she was saying.",
    "duration": 3001,
    "startTime": 156405,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And she said \"Yes, that's former\nVice President Al Gore",
    "duration": 2679,
    "startTime": 159430,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and his wife, Tipper.\"",
    "duration": 1843,
    "startTime": 162133,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And the man said,",
    "duration": 1527,
    "startTime": 164000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "\"He's come down a long way, hasn't he?\"",
    "duration": 2192,
    "startTime": 165551,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 4908,
    "startTime": 167767,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Applause)",
    "duration": 4277,
    "startTime": 172699,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "There's been kind\nof a series of epiphanies.",
    "duration": 3119,
    "startTime": 177000,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1144,
    "startTime": 180143,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "The very next day,\ncontinuing the totally true story,",
    "duration": 3665,
    "startTime": 181311,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I got on a G-V to fly to Africa\nto make a speech in Nigeria,",
    "duration": 5976,
    "startTime": 185000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "in the city of Lagos,\non the topic of energy.",
    "duration": 2856,
    "startTime": 191000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And I began the speech\nby telling them the story",
    "duration": 3796,
    "startTime": 194301,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "of what had just happened\nthe day before in Nashville.",
    "duration": 2713,
    "startTime": 198121,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And I told it pretty much the same way\nI've just shared it with you:",
    "duration": 3306,
    "startTime": 201196,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Tipper and I were driving ourselves,",
    "duration": 1738,
    "startTime": 204526,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Shoney's, low-cost\nfamily restaurant chain,",
    "duration": 2038,
    "startTime": 206288,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "what the man said -- they laughed.",
    "duration": 1933,
    "startTime": 208350,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I gave my speech, then went back\nout to the airport to fly back home.",
    "duration": 3583,
    "startTime": 210703,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I fell asleep on the plane",
    "duration": 1866,
    "startTime": 214310,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "until, during the middle\nof the night, we landed",
    "duration": 2538,
    "startTime": 216200,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "on the Azores Islands for refueling.",
    "duration": 2214,
    "startTime": 218762,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I woke up, they opened the door,\nI went out to get some fresh air,",
    "duration": 3112,
    "startTime": 221364,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and I looked, and there was a man\nrunning across the runway.",
    "duration": 3476,
    "startTime": 224500,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And he was waving a piece\nof paper, and he was yelling,",
    "duration": 3055,
    "startTime": 228000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "\"Call Washington! Call Washington!\"",
    "duration": 4074,
    "startTime": 231079,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And I thought to myself,\nin the middle of the night,",
    "duration": 2445,
    "startTime": 235981,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "in the middle of the Atlantic,",
    "duration": 1436,
    "startTime": 238450,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "what in the world could be\nwrong in Washington?",
    "duration": 2220,
    "startTime": 239910,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Then I remembered\nit could be a bunch of things.",
    "duration": 2261,
    "startTime": 242154,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 5537,
    "startTime": 244439,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "But what it turned out to be,",
    "duration": 1927,
    "startTime": 250000,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "was that my staff was extremely upset",
    "duration": 3311,
    "startTime": 251951,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "because one of the wire services\nin Nigeria had already written a story",
    "duration": 6202,
    "startTime": 255286,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "about my speech,",
    "duration": 1420,
    "startTime": 261512,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and it had already been printed in cities",
    "duration": 1976,
    "startTime": 262956,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "all across the United States of America.",
    "duration": 2332,
    "startTime": 264956,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It was printed in Monterey, I checked.",
    "duration": 1828,
    "startTime": 267312,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1150,
    "startTime": 269164,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "And the story began,",
    "duration": 2661,
    "startTime": 270553,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "\"Former Vice President Al Gore\nannounced in Nigeria yesterday,\" quote:",
    "duration": 4293,
    "startTime": 273238,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "'My wife Tipper and I have opened\na low-cost family restaurant'\" --",
    "duration": 3629,
    "startTime": 277555,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1642,
    "startTime": 281208,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "\"'named Shoney's,",
    "duration": 1348,
    "startTime": 282874,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "and we are running it ourselves.'\"",
    "duration": 1799,
    "startTime": 284246,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 3320,
    "startTime": 286069,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Before I could get back to U.S. soil,",
    "duration": 2158,
    "startTime": 289413,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "David Letterman and Jay Leno\nhad already started in on --",
    "duration": 4114,
    "startTime": 291595,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "one of them had me\nin a big white chef's hat,",
    "duration": 3243,
    "startTime": 295733,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Tipper was saying,\n\"One more burger with fries!\"",
    "duration": 2429,
    "startTime": 299000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 1047,
    "startTime": 301453,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Three days later,",
    "duration": 1282,
    "startTime": 302524,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I got a nice, long, handwritten letter",
    "duration": 2739,
    "startTime": 303830,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "from my friend and partner\nand colleague Bill Clinton, saying,",
    "duration": 3421,
    "startTime": 306593,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "\"Congratulations\non the new restaurant, Al!\"",
    "duration": 2396,
    "startTime": 310038,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 6673,
    "startTime": 312458,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "We like to celebrate\neach other's successes in life.",
    "duration": 3137,
    "startTime": 319155,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Laughter)",
    "duration": 5397,
    "startTime": 322316,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I was going to talk\nabout information ecology.",
    "duration": 2547,
    "startTime": 328606,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "But I was thinking that,",
    "duration": 2018,
    "startTime": 331177,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "since I plan to make a lifelong habit\nof coming back to TED,",
    "duration": 3757,
    "startTime": 333219,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "that maybe I could talk\nabout that another time.",
    "duration": 2693,
    "startTime": 337000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "(Applause)",
    "duration": 1400,
    "startTime": 339717,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Chris Anderson: It's a deal!",
    "duration": 1397,
    "startTime": 341141,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "(Applause)",
    "duration": 2626,
    "startTime": 342562,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Al Gore: I want to focus\non what many of you have said",
    "duration": 4518,
    "startTime": 345212,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "you would like me to elaborate on:",
    "duration": 1866,
    "startTime": 349754,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "What can you do about the climate crisis?",
    "duration": 3817,
    "startTime": 351644,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I want to start with a couple of --",
    "duration": 3339,
    "startTime": 356317,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I'm going to show some new images,",
    "duration": 2569,
    "startTime": 359680,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and I'm going to recapitulate\njust four or five.",
    "duration": 5123,
    "startTime": 362273,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Now, the slide show.",
    "duration": 1572,
    "startTime": 368075,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I update the slide show\nevery time I give it.",
    "duration": 3305,
    "startTime": 369671,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I add new images,",
    "duration": 1237,
    "startTime": 373000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "because I learn more about it\nevery time I give it.",
    "duration": 2905,
    "startTime": 374261,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It's like beach-combing, you know?",
    "duration": 1951,
    "startTime": 377823,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Every time the tide comes in and out,\nyou find some more shells.",
    "duration": 3178,
    "startTime": 379798,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Just in the last two days, we got\nthe new temperature records in January.",
    "duration": 5983,
    "startTime": 383000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "This is just for\nthe United States of America.",
    "duration": 3010,
    "startTime": 389007,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Historical average\nfor Januarys is 31 degrees;",
    "duration": 2738,
    "startTime": 392041,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "last month was 39.5 degrees.",
    "duration": 3684,
    "startTime": 394803,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Now, I know that you wanted some more\nbad news about the environment --",
    "duration": 4813,
    "startTime": 398932,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "I'm kidding.",
    "duration": 1168,
    "startTime": 403769,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "But these are the recapitulation slides,",
    "duration": 3056,
    "startTime": 405404,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and then I'm going to go into new\nmaterial about what you can do.",
    "duration": 3394,
    "startTime": 408484,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "But I wanted to elaborate\non a couple of these.",
    "duration": 2395,
    "startTime": 411902,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "First of all, this is where\nwe're projected to go",
    "duration": 3311,
    "startTime": 414321,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "with the U.S. contribution\nto global warming,",
    "duration": 2102,
    "startTime": 417656,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "under business as usual.",
    "duration": 1784,
    "startTime": 419782,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Efficiency in end-use electricity\nand end-use of all energy",
    "duration": 5386,
    "startTime": 421590,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "is the low-hanging fruit.",
    "duration": 1624,
    "startTime": 427000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Efficiency and conservation --\nit's not a cost; it's a profit.",
    "duration": 4504,
    "startTime": 428648,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "The sign is wrong.",
    "duration": 2677,
    "startTime": 433176,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It's not negative; it's positive.",
    "duration": 2143,
    "startTime": 435877,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "These are investments\nthat pay for themselves.",
    "duration": 2840,
    "startTime": 438044,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "But they are also very effective\nin deflecting our path.",
    "duration": 3871,
    "startTime": 440908,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Cars and trucks -- I talked\nabout that in the slideshow,",
    "duration": 3995,
    "startTime": 445620,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "but I want you to put it in perspective.",
    "duration": 2492,
    "startTime": 449639,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It's an easy, visible target of concern --",
    "duration": 4597,
    "startTime": 452893,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and it should be --",
    "duration": 1462,
    "startTime": 457514,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "but there is more global warming pollution\nthat comes from buildings",
    "duration": 4679,
    "startTime": 459000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "than from cars and trucks.",
    "duration": 1722,
    "startTime": 463703,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Cars and trucks are very significant,",
    "duration": 2641,
    "startTime": 466000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and we have the lowest\nstandards in the world.",
    "duration": 2585,
    "startTime": 468665,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And so we should address that.\nBut it's part of the puzzle.",
    "duration": 3026,
    "startTime": 471274,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Other transportation efficiency\nis as important as cars and trucks.",
    "duration": 5361,
    "startTime": 474324,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Renewables at the current levels\nof technological efficiency",
    "duration": 4342,
    "startTime": 479709,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "can make this much difference.",
    "duration": 1747,
    "startTime": 484075,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And with what Vinod, and John Doerr\nand others, many of you here --",
    "duration": 5955,
    "startTime": 485846,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "there are a lot of people\ndirectly involved in this --",
