    "content": "this wedge is going to grow\nmuch more rapidly",
    "duration": 2532,
    "startTime": 494416,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "than the current projection shows it.",
    "duration": 2187,
    "startTime": 496972,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Carbon Capture and Sequestration --\nthat's what CCS stands for --",
    "duration": 5740,
    "startTime": 499183,
    "startOfParagraph": false
