  {
    "content": "to continue to use fossil fuels\nin a way that is safe.",
    "duration": 6411,
    "startTime": 511786,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Not quite there yet.",
    "duration": 1336,
    "startTime": 519459,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "OK. Now, what can you do?",
    "duration": 3166,
    "startTime": 520819,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Reduce emissions in your home.",
    "duration": 1757,
    "startTime": 526495,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Most of these expenditures\nare also profitable.",
    "duration": 4198,
    "startTime": 529022,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Insulation, better design.",
    "duration": 1969,
    "startTime": 534007,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Buy green electricity where you can.",
    "duration": 2689,
    "startTime": 536000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I mentioned automobiles -- buy a hybrid.",
    "duration": 3810,
    "startTime": 539436,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Use light rail.",
    "duration": 1706,
    "startTime": 543270,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Figure out some of the other options\nthat are much better.",
    "duration": 2782,
    "startTime": 545505,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It's important.",
    "duration": 1165,
    "startTime": 548311,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Be a green consumer.",
    "duration": 1719,
    "startTime": 550254,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "You have choices with everything you buy,",
    "duration": 2979,
    "startTime": 551997,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "between things that have a harsh effect,",
    "duration": 3607,
    "startTime": 555000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "or a much less harsh effect\non the global climate crisis.",
    "duration": 5500,
    "startTime": 558631,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Consider this:",
    "duration": 1832,
    "startTime": 564870,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Make a decision to live\na carbon-neutral life.",
    "duration": 3252,
    "startTime": 566726,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Those of you who are good at branding,",
    "duration": 2434,
    "startTime": 570663,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I'd love to get your advice and help",
    "duration": 2472,
    "startTime": 573121,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "on how to say this in a way\nthat connects with the most people.",
    "duration": 6078,
    "startTime": 575617,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It is easier than you think.",
    "duration": 1981,
    "startTime": 581719,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It really is.",
    "duration": 1316,
    "startTime": 583724,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "A lot of us in here\nhave made that decision,",
    "duration": 3395,
    "startTime": 587223,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and it is really pretty easy.",
    "duration": 2134,
    "startTime": 590642,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It means reduce\nyour carbon dioxide emissions",
    "duration": 5927,
    "startTime": 592800,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "with the full range\nof choices that you make,",
    "duration": 2696,
    "startTime": 598751,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and then purchase or acquire offsets",
    "duration": 4125,
    "startTime": 601471,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "for the remainder that you have not\ncompletely reduced.",
    "duration": 3117,
    "startTime": 605620,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And what it means is elaborated\nat climatecrisis.net.",
    "duration": 6490,
    "startTime": 608761,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "There is a carbon calculator.",
    "duration": 2865,
    "startTime": 615755,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Participant Productions convened --",
    "duration": 3475,
    "startTime": 619501,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "with my active involvement --",
    "duration": 2570,
    "startTime": 623000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "the leading software writers in the world,",
    "duration": 2817,
    "startTime": 625594,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "on this arcane science\nof carbon calculation,",
    "duration": 3303,
    "startTime": 628435,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to construct a consumer-friendly\ncarbon calculator.",
    "duration": 4102,
    "startTime": 631762,
    "startOfParagraph": false
