  {
    "content": "You can very precisely calculate\nwhat your CO2 emissions are,",
    "duration": 6209,
    "startTime": 636317,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and then you will be given\noptions to reduce.",
    "duration": 3318,
    "startTime": 642550,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And by the time the movie\ncomes out in May,",
    "duration": 3197,
    "startTime": 645892,
    "startOfParagraph": false
