    "duration": 1863,
    "startTime": 649113,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and we will have click-through\npurchases of offsets.",
    "duration": 3434,
    "startTime": 651000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Next, consider making\nyour business carbon-neutral.",
    "duration": 3222,
    "startTime": 655000,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Again, some of us have done that,",
