    "startTime": 692807,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And if they judge how much\nthey're going to get paid",
    "duration": 4693,
    "startTime": 696736,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "on your capital that they've invested,",
    "duration": 3300,
    "startTime": 701453,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
