    "duration": 1943,
    "startTime": 704777,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "you're going to get short-term decisions.",
    "duration": 2316,
    "startTime": 706744,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "A lot more to be said about that.",
    "duration": 1613,
    "startTime": 710999,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Become a catalyst of change.",
    "duration": 1746,
    "startTime": 712636,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "Teach others, learn about it,\ntalk about it.",
    "duration": 3635,
    "startTime": 714406,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "The movie is a movie version\nof the slideshow",
    "duration": 3405,
    "startTime": 719263,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I gave two nights ago,\nexcept it's a lot more entertaining.",
    "duration": 2919,
    "startTime": 722692,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And it comes out in May.",
    "duration": 2147,
    "startTime": 726694,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
