    "duration": 3961,
    "startTime": 729437,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Consider sending somebody to Nashville.",
    "duration": 3603,
    "startTime": 735106,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Pick well.",
    "duration": 1155,
    "startTime": 739390,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And I am personally going to train people\nto give this slideshow --",
    "duration": 4446,
    "startTime": 741381,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "re-purposed, with some\nof the personal stories obviously replaced",
    "duration": 4755,
    "startTime": 745851,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "with a generic approach,",
    "duration": 2070,
    "startTime": 750630,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and it's not just the slides,\nit's what they mean.",
