    "startTime": 752724,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And it's how they link together.",
    "duration": 1601,
    "startTime": 755447,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And so I'm going to be conducting\na course this summer",
    "duration": 4587,
    "startTime": 757072,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "for a group of people that are\nnominated by different folks",
    "duration": 3835,
    "startTime": 761683,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to come and then give it en masse,",
    "duration": 2229,
    "startTime": 765542,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "in communities all across the country,",
    "duration": 2181,
    "startTime": 767795,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and we're going to update the slideshow\nfor all of them every single week,",
    "duration": 4665,
    "startTime": 770000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to keep it right on the cutting edge.",
    "duration": 3031,
    "startTime": 774689,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Working with Larry Lessig, it will be,\nsomewhere in that process,",
    "duration": 3881,
    "startTime": 777744,
