    "content": "It doesn't mean\nthat if you're a Republican,",
    "duration": 2090,
    "startTime": 799060,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "that I'm trying to convince you\nto be a Democrat.",
    "duration": 2324,
    "startTime": 801174,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We need Republicans as well.",
    "duration": 1505,
    "startTime": 803935,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "This used to be a bipartisan issue,",
    "duration": 2009,
    "startTime": 805464,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "and I know that\nin this group it really is.",
    "duration": 2457,
    "startTime": 807497,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Become politically active.",
    "duration": 1552,
    "startTime": 809978,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Make our democracy work the way\nit's supposed to work.",
    "duration": 2873,
    "startTime": 811554,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Support the idea of capping\ncarbon dioxide emissions --",
    "duration": 5549,
    "startTime": 814753,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "global warming pollution --\nand trading it.",
    "duration": 2015,
    "startTime": 820326,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Here's why: as long as the United States\nis out of the world system,",
