    "startTime": 827000,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Once it becomes a closed system,\nwith U.S. participation,",
    "duration": 4047,
    "startTime": 828692,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "then everybody\nwho's on a board of directors --",
    "duration": 2223,
    "startTime": 832763,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "how many people here\nserve on the board of directors",
