  {
    "content": "you will have legal liability\nif you do not urge your CEO",
    "duration": 6237,
    "startTime": 841865,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to get the maximum income from reducing\nand trading the carbon emissions",
    "duration": 4127,
    "startTime": 848126,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "that can be avoided.",
    "duration": 1309,
    "startTime": 852277,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "The market will work\nto solve this problem --",
    "duration": 2665,
    "startTime": 853610,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "if we can accomplish this.",
    "duration": 2217,
    "startTime": 858949,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Help with the mass persuasion campaign\nthat will start this spring.",
    "duration": 3385,
    "startTime": 862434,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We have to change the minds\nof the American people.",
    "duration": 2508,
    "startTime": 865843,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Because presently, the politicians\ndo not have permission",
    "duration": 2759,
    "startTime": 868375,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "to do what needs to be done.",
    "duration": 1919,
    "startTime": 871158,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "And in our modern country, the role\nof logic and reason no longer includes",
