    "startTime": 873355,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "mediating between wealth and power\nthe way it once did.",
    "duration": 2954,
    "startTime": 878833,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "It's now repetition of short, hot-button,\n30-second, 28-second television ads.",
    "duration": 5560,
    "startTime": 881811,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "We have to buy a lot of those ads.",
    "duration": 1858,
    "startTime": 887395,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Let's re-brand global warming,\nas many of you have suggested.",
    "duration": 4310,
    "startTime": 890221,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "I like \"climate crisis\"\ninstead of \"climate collapse,\"",
    "duration": 2869,
    "startTime": 894555,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "but again, those of you\nwho are good at branding,",
    "duration": 2327,
    "startTime": 897448,
    "startOfParagraph": false
