    "startTime": 918160,
    "startOfParagraph": true
  },
  {
    "content": "this is not a political issue.",
    "duration": 2165,
    "startTime": 921584,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Again, the Republicans here --\nthis shouldn't be partisan.",
