    "startTime": 923773,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "You have more influence\nthan some of us who are Democrats do.",
    "duration": 3640,
    "startTime": 929336,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "This is an opportunity.",
    "duration": 1476,
    "startTime": 933421,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
    "content": "Not just this, but connected\nto the ideas that are here,",
    "duration": 4852,
    "startTime": 934921,
    "startOfParagraph": false
  },
  {
